reviewText: This is an awsome dance video, it has two or three different dance routines on the video. My 8 year old loves it and had me to play it during her 8th birthday party we had here at home. But I am still having a problem getting the steps to the main dance routine with the ballroom step, I will keep trying until I get it, so that I will be able to teach others at my church and maybe get a dancexercise class going.

This work out video is slow paced and easy to follow. It is fun and the music is great. This work out video can be used by people of all ages.
I love to dance, and this video gave me another dance to add to my repertoire of dance routines.  It is so much fun to me.

This video truly gives you the maximum workout.  It works every part of your body and all in fun.  Vicky Winans and her trainer talks you through every step to lose the weight that you want.  They give you time to rest in between each exercise.  This is an exceptional workout video expect to lose weight with continual use.  I can see results in my stomach and buttock area after just 2 weeks.

I thought that since Vickie Winans does have such a great personality this would be an ideal video for me.  She is so entertaining when she is doing interviews and other performances that I thought for sure I would enjoy this video, but I don't.  She tries to be funny, but she is not.  The up side is that I do love the excercises!!  They are awesome and will help you attain your goal, but I don't watch the video to do the workout.  I do them from memory because I dislike the video just that much!!
